It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:

<blockquote>Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like pi&#241;a coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)</blockquote>

...or something like this:

<blockquote>The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.</blockquote>

As a new WordPress user, you should go to <a href="http://localhost/callie-britt/wp-admin/">your dashboard</a> to delete this page and create new pages for your content. <ol>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">1</span>The family is the singular most significant factor influencing human identity.</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">2</span>Family-based therapy is a powerful model for change, one that not only helps people cope with major life issues, but that can ultimately transform how we lead our lives, resulting in healthier communities and societies,resulting in healthier communities and societies.</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">3</span>Quality mental health care should be available to all who need it regardless of their financial resources.</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">4</span>Today "family" takes many forms and is comprised of people joined together by biology, intentionality and/or law.</li>
</ol>
<p>[/vc_column_text][/trx_sc_content][vc_empty_space height="2em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces" equal_height="yes"][vc_column fix_column="" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" icons_position="left" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_single_image image="371" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces" equal_height="yes"][vc_column fix_column="" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" icons_position="left" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_empty_space height="2em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_content size="none" margins="large" number_position="br" title_style="default" link_style="default"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" link_style="default" title="My Core Values ||and Beliefs" subtitle="Beliefs &amp; Values"][vc_column_text]</p>
<ol>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">1</span>The family is the singular most significant factor influencing human identity.</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">2</span>Family-based therapy is a powerful model for change, one that not only helps people cope with major life issues, but that can ultimately transform how we lead our lives, resulting in healthier communities and societies,resulting in healthier communities and societies.</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">3</span>Quality mental health care should be available to all who need it regardless of their financial resources.</li>
<li><span style="font-weight: normal;">4</span>Today "family" takes many forms and is comprised of people joined together by biology, intentionality and/or law.</li>
</ol>

In doing so, offer you techniques to help you to learn a new set of behaviours, and help you to practice this new skill until it has become embedded. You’ll also be given helpful “homework” in the form of practicing your new skills. In the process, you should experience an improvement in your symptoms. The goal of CBT is a relatively rapid improvement and the cessation of therapy within 16 weeks, but each case is unique and the duration may vary from person to person.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="2.5em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/trx_sc_content][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" icons_position="left" css=".vc_custom_1531217690856{background-color: #f3f2ee !important;}" offset="vc_hidden-sm vc_hidden-xs"][trx_sc_content size="none" margins="large" number_position="br" title_style="default" link_style="default"][vc_empty_space height="4.6em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" link_style="default" title="If you Experiencing One of the Following Symptoms:" subtitle="Strategies for an emotional problems"][vc_empty_space height="1.6em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]</p>
<ul class="trx_addons_list_dot">
<li>Feeling Depressed, Feeling Stressed</li>
<li>Battling With Anxiety, Panic Attacks or a Phobia</li>
<li>Having Relationship Problems but are Unsure How to Move Forward</li>
<li>Experiencing an Eating Disorder</li>
<li>Weighed Down by Obsessive Rituals, Compulsive Checking or Hoarding</li>
</ul>
<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4.8em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_empty_space height="1.8em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][trx_sc_button type="default" color_style="link2" new_window="" icon_position="left" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="" link="/appoinments" title="Make an Appointment"][/trx_sc_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile=""][vc_column hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" icons_position="left" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][vc_single_image image="363" img_size="full"][trx_sc_content size="none" paddings="large" number_position="br" title_style="default" link_style="default" css=".vc_custom_1529567526657{background-color: #7fb98d !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="1.7em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_align="left" link_style="default" scheme="dark" title="What to Expect" subtitle="Expectations" css=".vc_custom_1529567596961{background-color: #7fb98d !important;}"][vc_empty_space height="2em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1529565498991{background-color: #7fb98d !important;}"]<span style="color: #ffffff;">In therapy we will discuss your problems and how they are currently affecting you. In doing so, offer you techniques to help you to learn a new set of behaviours, and help you to practice this new skill until it has become embedded. You’ll also be given helpful “homework” in the form of practicing your new skills. In the process, you should experience an improvement in your symptoms. The goal of CBT is a relatively rapid improvement and the cessation of therapy within 16 weeks, but each case is unique and the duration may vary from person to person.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="2.5em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][/trx_sc_content][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height="yes"][vc_column hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile="" icons_position="left" offset="vc_hidden-lg vc_hidden-md"][trx_sc_content size="none" paddings="large" number_position="br" title_style="default" link_style="default" css=".vc_custom_1531219545229{background-color: #f3f2ee !important;}"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" link_style="default" title="If you Experiencing One of the Following Symptoms:" subtitle="Strategies for an emotional problems"][vc_empty_space height="1.5em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text el_class="about2_different_list"]</p>
<ul class="trx_addons_list_dot">
<li>Feeling Depressed, Feeling Stressed</li>
<li>Battling With Anxiety, Panic Attacks or a Phobia</li>
<li>Having Relationship Problems but are Unsure How to Move Forward</li>
<li>Experiencing an Eating Disorder</li>
<li>Weighed Down by Obsessive Rituals, Compulsive Checking or Hoarding</li>
</ul>

<h5><span style="color: #515855;">Marriage and family therapy is:</span></h5>
<ul class="trx_addons_list_parameters">
<li>Brief</li>
<li>Solution-focused</li>
<li>Specific, with attainable therapeutic goals</li>
<li>Designed with the "end in mind"</li>
</ul>

<h5><span style="color: #515855;">Marriage and family therapy is:</span></h5>
<ul class="trx_addons_list_parameters">
<li>Brief</li>
<li>Solution-focused</li>
<li>Specific, with attainable therapeutic goals</li>
<li>Designed with the "end in mind"</li>
</ul>

<h6 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #707170;">Make your relationship work by following</span><br />
<span style="color: #707170;">these 5 basic principles</span></h6>
<p>[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_services type="timeline" featured="number" featured_position="top" no_links="" hide_excerpt="" no_margin="" popup="" orderby="post_date" order="desc" title_style="default" link_style="default" count="3" columns="3"][trx_sc_services type="timeline" featured="number" featured_position="top" no_links="" hide_excerpt="" no_margin="" popup="" orderby="post_date" order="desc" slider="" title_style="default" link_style="default" count="2" columns="3" offset="3"][vc_empty_space height="7.7em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_empty_space height="5.7em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement="middle" hide_bg_image_on_tablet="" hide_bg_image_on_mobile=""][vc_column icons_position="left"][vc_empty_space height="8.8em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_single_image image="341" img_size="full"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_empty_space height="0.5em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile="1"][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="1" hide_on_notebook="1" hide_on_tablet="1" hide_on_mobile=""][trx_sc_title title_style="default" link_style="default" title="Why use a Marriage and Family Therapist?" subtitle="Why use therapist"][vc_empty_space height="3.5em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]Research studies repeatedly demonstrate the effectiveness of marriage and family therapy in treating the full range of mental and emotional disorders and health problems. Adolescent drug abuse, depression, alcoholism, obesity and dementia in the elderly -- as well as marital distress and conflict -- are just some of the conditions Marriage and Family Therapists effectively treat. Studies also show that clients are highly satisfied with services of Marriage and Family Therapists[/vc_column_text][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="#dbdbdb" css=".vc_custom_1529936879606{margin-top: 4em !important;margin-bottom: 4em !important;}"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner icons_position="left" offset="vc_col-lg-6 vc_col-md-6"][vc_column_text css=".vc_custom_1529936958828{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0.5em !important;}"]</p>

<h2>Map</h2>
<div class="dummy"></div>
<p>[/vc_column_text][trx_sc_googlemap style="default" zoom="14" height="327px" prevent_scroll="" markers="%5B%7B%22address%22%3A%22350%205th%20Ave%2C%20New%20York%2C%20NY%2010118%2C%20USA%22%2C%22icon%22%3A%22266%22%2C%22animation%22%3A%22none%22%7D%5D" title_style="default" link_style="default"][/trx_sc_googlemap][/vc_column][/vc_row]</p>
";s:10:"post_title";s:10:"Shortcodes";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:10:"shortcodes";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2018-08-20 13:47:01";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2018-08-20 13:47:01";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:42:"http://localhost/callie-britt/?page_id=237";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"page";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:158;a:23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"239";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-09-26 11:53:32";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-09-26 11:53:32";s:12:"post_content";s:5047:"[vc_row][vc_column icons_position="left"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h3" title_align="center" link_style="default" title="Our Support Policy"][vc_empty_space height="3em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_column_text]
<ul>
 	<li>To get a pre-purchase advice, you may post in the theme’s forum.</li>
 	<li>To get a response more promptly, you are recommended to use our Ticket-system.</li>
 	<li>We try to answer your questions within 1-10 hours. However, if any delay occurs, it doesn’t mean that we forgot about you. Some of the issues require testing and analyzing, so we can resolve it effectively.</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_column_text]
<ul>
 	<li>Please note! We do not provide support, if you do not have the purchase code.</li>
 	<li>Item support does not include:
<ol>
 	<li>Customization and installation.</li>
 	<li>Support for third party software and plugins.</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ul>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column icons_position="left"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h3" title_align="center" link_style="default" title="How to use our Support System"][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_single_image image="317" img_size="large"][vc_empty_space alter_height="medium" hide_on_mobile=""][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
 	<li>In the ‘Item Details’ there is a clickable banner “Support Sys”, which leads you to tickets.</li>
 	<li>Or you may simply follow this link: <a href="https://ancorathemes.ticksy.com/">ancorathemes.ticksy.com</a>.</li>
 	<li>Enter your purchase key and register in the system.</li>
 	<li>To avoid a confusion, please use your own ThemeForest login in Support System.</li>
 	<li>Fill out the ticket form.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column icons_position="left"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h3" title_align="center" link_style="default" title="How to find a purchase key"][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_single_image image="318" img_size="large"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_column_text]
<ol>
 	<li>Open the “downloads” tab in your account.</li>
 	<li>Find our theme in the list of products.</li>
 	<li>Click “download” button, and in the drop-down menu select “license certificate &amp; purchase code”.</li>
</ol>
[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_separator][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column icons_position="left"][trx_sc_title title_style="default" title_tag="h3" title_align="center" link_style="default" title="Recommended Hosting"][vc_empty_space height="1.5em" alter_height="none" hide_on_desktop="" hide_on_notebook="" hide_on_tablet="" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_column_text]Ancora offers only the best products and services and recommends them to their customers. One of the most important services is HOSTING. Unlike any cheap hostings that usually have limited resources which causes many problems to the site owners, quality hosting gives a client a fair amount of resources sufficient for any website and any task. By using quality hosting you can rest assured that your site will work smoothly. If you happen to use such hosting with limited resources (e.g. GoDaddy!), you may experience issues with “one-click install” feature. In that case, you are always welcome to contact our support team to get qualified help.[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="4em" alter_height="none" hide_on_mobile=""][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2" icons_position="left"][vc_single_image image="320" img_size="large" alignment="center" onclick="custom_link" img_link_target="_blank" link="https://secure1.inmotionhosting.com/cgi-bin/gby/clickthru.cgi?id=themerex"][vc_column_text]
